      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not even about resting anymore. i've rested. i've tried everything. but the loop just resets. it's like i'm a character in a game that's just a glitch. nothing i do changes the outcome. it just feels like the only way to actually stop the cycle is to just... not be here for it. to just exit.",
